{"tid":1661621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，同我記熟呢堆名佢！","createTime":"2019-10-18T08:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T16:15:12.000Z","uid":321682,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0cff53e7a56b84276780e9c18a54cb9937cf8ae9","tid":1661621,"uid":321682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:03:18.000Z","msg":"我明白要記得晒邊d舖要罷買，邊d要幫襯唔係一件易事<br />\n所以我參考左幾個有心人整嘅app同網頁 (包括：WhatsGap、新時代消費地圖、黃藍商戶地圖、全民罷買日、Words of Mouth信)，整左呢一系列嘅圖，方便大家<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一眼睇晒要<ins>重點打擊</ins>嘅大品牌</span></span></strong>。我仲開左個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">IG page叫「罷買指南」 @bamaiguide</span></span></strong>，方便大家搵返呢d圖。我亦會keep住喺IG更新每個類別，同增加唔同類別嘅品牌：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JeyXdOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJeyXdOm.jpg&h=3cbbaa4d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ON9n9mE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FON9n9mE.jpg&h=d66dd8e7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rcXEr8k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrcXEr8k.jpg&h=9a3a677d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KfoDHGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKfoDHGF.jpg&h=111206a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n(持續更新中)<br />\n<br />\n唔係要針對大公司/大品牌，而係呢堆商戶有以下特色：<br />\n深紅色資本 / 所屬大集團嘅老闆曾經公開撐警 / 曾經禁止員工罷工或遊行 / 曾經無理解僱黃絲員工 / 一直有濃厚深藍形象 / 曾經禁止示威者或黑衣人幫襯<br />\n<br />\n大家一定一定要認得佢地d logo同舖頭名，以後喺街見到都要避之則吉！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">因為呢d大財團、大牌子賺賺埋埋咁多錢，結果喺關鍵時候出賣香港人、向警察獻媚、與民為敵！</span><br />\n就算大家未記得晒邊d係藍店、邊d係黃店，都一定要記得佢地！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地期待煲底除罩相見嘅一日，亦都要期待呢堆麻木不仁嘅舖頭執Q晒嘅一日！</span></strong><br />\nP牌推唔郁，同我推爆佢！"},{"pid":"c5b8327fa69237e196f4d299b67ba02bef963487","tid":1661621,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命文宣圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akqjfDV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akqjfDV</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度仲有一單近期爆出嘅核彈新聞，係關於中共高層貪污新聞，直刺中共心臟，希望都可以唸辦法向強國人宣傳一下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/mDLryDX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mDLryDX</a>"},{"pid":"7e869d6b3d5d1c11ccdd2edc44553416943355c2","tid":1661621,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"ecb8ec3a580b5c5c55637961807895709eff9793","tid":1661621,"uid":293514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"搵唔到個IG嘅？"},{"pid":"cd9e40dc9c0e2bc63d9e98236f628c0c4cb4f557","tid":1661621,"uid":5451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecb8ec3a580b5c5c55637961807895709eff9793","tid":1661621,"uid":293514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T00:59:57.000Z","msg":"搵唔到個IG嘅？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"886af2e850bcadaa8ffe22f72ada23e8548c4bfd","tid":1661621,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:57:50.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"75140f0d8a729618da1acef29372c6fabdd8a4ca","tid":1661621,"uid":42943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T01:58:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4f84f26f606329503858e2bbc30e5d89924315d","tid":1661621,"uid":247554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd9e40dc9c0e2bc63d9e98236f628c0c4cb4f557","tid":1661621,"uid":5451,"like":0,"dis